data.description: Come and check out this newly renovated Cape Cod home. This cozy home is conveniently located right by the bases, highway, and the bay! First floor primary bedroom opens up to the newly renovated primary bathroom of your dreams which includes a beautiful walk in shower, large sink vanity, shiplap wall feature and a freestanding bathtub. The kitchen also has been fully updated with butcher block countertops and all new kitchen appliances. Large/ private backyard with a detached garage that is wired and can be used for excellent outdoor entertaining. With no flood insurance required, this home offers it all. Come and check out this cozy Cape Cod home today!
